com.netflix.governator.test

Class TracingProvisionListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.netflix.governator.test.TracingProvisionListener

  • public class TracingProvisionListener
extends java.lang.Object
    Use TracingProvisionListener to debug issues with Guice Injector creation by tracing the object initialization path. Various hooks are provided for the different stages of object instantiation: before, after and on error. To enable add the following binding in any guice module bindListener(Matchers.any(), TracingProvisionListener.createDefault());
